<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450032>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Pimelodella yaharo, CZUT-IC 10922, holotype, 74.7 mm SL, Colombia, Departamento La Guajira, Dibulla, Río Jeréz. Left lateral, dorsal and ventral views, respecticvelly." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450032/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450036>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ventral view of cleared and stained right pectoral-fin spine of a) Pimelodella yaharo, CZUT-IC 15262, paratype, 76.9 mm SL; b) Pimelodella chagresi, ANSP 151046, 76.3 mm SL; c) Pimelodella floridablancaensis, CZUT-IC 225, 91.4 mm SL; d) Pimelodella reyesi, CZUT-IC 17838, 88.6 mm SL; e) Pimelodella grisea, CZUT-IC 17825, 118.6 mm SL. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450036/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450038>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distribution of Pimelodella yaharo in Río Jerez and Río Cañas, coastal drainages of the Sierra Nevada de Santa Marta, Colombia. Black star: type locality; black circle: locality in Río Cañas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450038/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3450042>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Habitat of Pimelodella yaharo, Colombia, Departamento La Guajira, Dibulla. A. Type locality, Río Jerez; B. Río Cañas." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3450042/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

